## 7. URL Design (New APIs)

- **Nouns** for resources (e.g. `/api/admin/artprom`, `/api/admin/artprom/{proId}/files`).
- **Actions** expressed by HTTP method: GET (read), POST (create), PUT/PATCH (update), DELETE (delete).
- Examples:
  - `POST   /api/admin/artprom` — create
  - `GET    /api/admin/artprom/{proId}` — get one
  - `DELETE /api/admin/artprom/{proId}/files/{fileId}/{seq}` — delete one file

